/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image presents a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades hinting at the architectural diversity of the city. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The sky itself is overcast, casting a soft, diffused light over the scene. The colors in the image are predominantly green, gray, and white, reflecting both the natural and man-made elements of the landscape.
